<TEXT>
<P>
Mary E. Keats of Van Nuys, who was manager of the hair styling department at 
Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer Studios for a decade, has died at the Motion Picture and 
Television Country House and Hospital in Woodland Hills. She was 70. 
</P>
<P>
