Keats worked on a free-lance basis for movie studios and television until her 
retirement in 1984. Through the years, she worked with many celebrities, 
including Elvis Presley, Eva Marie Saint, Liza Minnelli, Debbie Reynolds, 
Luciano Pavarotti and Burt Reynolds. She also traveled with Bob Hope during the 
Korean War. 
</P>
<P>
