REFUGEES -- JORDAN; JORDAN -- TRAVEL RESTRICTIONS; IRAQ -- BORDERS -- JORDAN; 
QUALITY OF LIFE; REFUGEES -- KUWAIT; RELOCATION OF PEOPLE; JORDAN -- FOREIGN 
POPULATIONS; IRAQ -- FOREIGN POPULATIONS 
</P>
