<HEADLINE>
<P>
VENTURA COUNTY NEWS ROUNDUP: COUNTYWIDE; 
</P>
<P>
OPINIONS SOUGHT ON CSU CAMPUS SITE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By GARY GORMAN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ventura County residents are invited to a meeting today to give their views on 
the location of a proposed California State University campus in the county. 
</P>
<P>
The meeting will begin at 9:30 a.m. at the Financial Plaza Hilton, 600 
Esplanade Drive, Oxnard. 
</P>
<P>
Cal State officials, a citizens committee and EIP Consultants are narrowing a 
list of 38 proposed sites to between three and five. When those are chosen in a 
month, the consultants will prepare environmental impact reports on each. GARY 
GORMAN 
</P>
