THEFTS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; KIDNAPINGS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; BURGLARIES -- 
LOS ANGELES COUNTY; RAPE -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; ROBBERIES -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
