<TEXT>
<P>
Pro-Iranian Muslim extremists in Lebanon today freed Irish hostage Brian Keenan 
after more than four years in captivity, Iran's official news agency said. 
</P>
<P>
"Irish hostage Brian Keenan has just been set free in Lebanon," the Islamic 
